Package net.ddns.mucaho.jnetrobust

Class Summary
Logger Abstract class which is able to handle protocol specific logging.
Protocol<T> The central API class that represents the virtual protocol.
ProtocolConfig<T> Configuration class which will be used to configure a protocol instance.
ProtocolListener<T> The listener which will be notified about specific protocol events.
 

Enum Summary
Logger.LoggingEvent Enum representing all possible logging event descriptions.
